{"TopicId":30347,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Not sure if this is new or not. But i just noticed it.","CreatedByName":"ZedNova","CreatedById":57175,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-30T23:40:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"ZedNova","CreatedById":57175,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-30T23:40:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHi, i have no idea if this feature has been in here awhile. But when you Hold Shift and press a direction key while on a ladder, your kerbal will turn his head in a way corresponding to the directional key you press. ( WASD )\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELooking up:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://assets-cloud.enjin.com/users/1465978/pics/original/1770085.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00221770085.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELooking right:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://assets-cloud.enjin.com/users/1465978/pics/original/1770086.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00221770086.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELooking Left:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://assets-cloud.enjin.com/users/1465978/pics/original/1770089.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00221770089.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0027s pretty cool.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fiddlestyx","CreatedById":57329,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-30T23:43:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENever knew that.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"E. F. Kranz","CreatedById":12617,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-30T23:45:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENeato!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ethis space intentionally left blank\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nhnifong","CreatedById":12196,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-30T23:48:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI think you discovered that first\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jjwb22101","CreatedById":64078,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-30T23:56:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYeah, I think that\u0027s a first. Definitely cool!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xandski","CreatedById":56858,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-30T23:56:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThats fantastic. It gives me some new ideas for frapsed stuff \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aetius194","CreatedById":57255,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-30T23:56:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThat\u0027s pretty cool.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HarvesteR","CreatedById":4,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T00:02:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAlso, if you press space while holding shift, you\u0027ll jump off the ladder in the direction you\u0027re leaning towards, instead of just letting go. It\u0027s called a push-off, works best in very low gravity. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECheers\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceisbeautifulul","CreatedById":68592,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T00:04:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThis is awesome! \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EA huge win for Kerbal Cenimatics. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZedNova","CreatedById":57175,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T00:06:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HarvesteR\u0022 data-cite=\u0022HarvesteR\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EAlso, if you press space while holding shift, you\u0027ll jump off the ladder in the direction you\u0027re leaning towards, instead of just letting go. It\u0027s called a push-off, works best in very low gravity. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECheers\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWow, that\u0027s Cool!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI can just imagine using this when i run out of fuel during my mun landings.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Jedi Master","CreatedById":57348,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T00:08:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENope, never knew that.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xandski","CreatedById":56858,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T00:17:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI wonder if there\u0027s there a way of controlling the Kerbal\u0027s expressions in game...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lumaro","CreatedById":55749,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T01:01:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI don\u0027t think this is new. I have been using this sense 0.19. There is just a limited amount of documentation on controls.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DisarmingBaton5","CreatedById":68576,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T01:23:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HarvesteR\u0022 data-cite=\u0022HarvesteR\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EAlso, if you press space while holding shift, you\u0027ll jump off the ladder in the direction you\u0027re leaning towards, instead of just letting go. It\u0027s called a push-off, works best in very low gravity. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECheers\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWOAH! ok, now I know what to do when my brand new, shiny aeroplane inevitably spontaneously plunges kerbinward!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEDIT: Can you push off backwards?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Peenvogel","CreatedById":59022,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T01:27:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENice find. I didn\u0027t know.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AmpsterMan","CreatedById":32671,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T01:49:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_ohmy.png\u0022 alt=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E :O \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_ohmy.png\u0022 alt=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E :O \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_ohmy.png\u0022 alt=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis changes the game COMPLETELY!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tremzack","CreatedById":27768,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T02:18:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAm I the only one that read all of the 0.16 changelog when it came out? Haha\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Itsdavyjones","CreatedById":57605,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T02:56:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWow, can\u0027t wait to try this out.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DisarmingBaton5","CreatedById":68576,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T04:23:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tremzack\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Tremzack\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EAm I the only one that read all of the 0.16 changelog when it came out? Haha\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt came with EVA originally? wow!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KevinTMC","CreatedById":28909,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T04:56:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI just tried this after landing on Minmus, and the only hitch was that Bill seemed to loosen his grip on the ladder a bit whenever I held down Shift. So I couldn\u0027t play around too much with the looking in different directions...he was sliding too steadily towards the ground.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHaving him take a dive backwards off the ladder was certainly fun though!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deadweasel","CreatedById":23123,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T05:21:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThat\u0027s amazing!!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlso, why isn\u0027t this in the wiki? \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Key_Bindings\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/Key_Bindings\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NeoMorph","CreatedById":58200,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T05:45:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spaceisbeautifulul\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Spaceisbeautifulul\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EThis is awesome! \u003Cp\u003EA huge win for Kerbal Cenimatics. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHell yeah, this is gonna be awesome for my comic series...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZedNova","CreatedById":57175,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T12:22:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESo it seems SQUAD put in this awhile ago, and forgot to tell us everything about it?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"superm18","CreatedById":57755,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T12:54:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENice! i knew about the jumping bit but not the looking around bit. Very cool! must be good when making video\u0027s\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-31T13:33:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENow to form the Kerbal Low-Grav Diving Team! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}